Required libraries:
  >=crypto++-5.6 (http://www.cryptopp.com/)
  >=boost-1.36


Compile lazy-random:
  $ mkdir build
  $ cd build
  $ ccmake ../.
  $ make
    
  The executable should be located at build/src/lazy-random.

Install lazy-random:
  Set up CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX at the ccmake phase.
  run a final
    $ make install
